-- Migration 072 — Tier 1 country installation history expansion
--
-- Compiled from:
--   • Wind onshore: WindEurope "Wind energy in Europe — Statistics & trends"
--     annual reports (2009-2025), GWEC Global Wind Reports (2010-2025),
--     IRENA Renewable Capacity Statistics 2025 (annual change tables),
--     national regulators: BNetzA Marktstammdatenregister (DE), REE/CNMC
--     statistical reports (ES), RTE Panorama de l'électricité renouvelable
--     (FR), Energistyrelsen Stamdataregister (DK), CBS / RVO (NL),
--     Terna anagrafica impianti (IT), Energimyndigheten (SE), URE Annual
--     Report (PL), ANEEL BIG (BR), AEMO/Clean Energy Council (AU),
--     CRE/CENACE/SENER (MX), TEİAŞ/EPDK (TR).
--   • Wind offshore: WindEurope offshore statistics (2009-2025), 4COffshore
--     and BNEF Offshore Wind Market Outlooks, BSH/BNetzA (DE),
--     Energistyrelsen offshore registry (DK), FPS Economy / Elia (BE),
--     RVO (NL), US BOEM Renewable Energy Programs Office, Taiwan MoEA
--     Bureau of Energy.
--   • Solar PV: IEA-PVPS "Snapshot of Global PV Markets" 2011-2025,
--     SolarPower Europe "Global Market Outlook" 2014-2025, Eurostat
--     nrg_inf_epc, BMWi/BNetzA (DE), REE / IDAE / UNEF (ES), Terna /
--     GSE (IT), RTE / SDES (FR), BEIS DUKES / Solar Energy UK (GB),
--     CBS / RVO (NL), APERe (BE), AEMO / Clean Energy Regulator (AU),
--     METI / ANRE FIT register (JP), EIA Form 860 (US).
--   • BESS: BNEF Energy Storage Market Outlook (1H/2H 2022-2025),
--     IEA Energy Storage Tracker, Wood Mackenzie Energy Storage Service,
--     EASE-Frith European Market Monitor on Energy Storage 2024,
--     Modo Energy GB BESS index, EIA Form 860 large-scale battery
--     register, Clean Energy Council BESS report (AU), Terna (IT),
--     KEPCO / KESIA (KR), METI ANRE (JP), Eirgrid DS3 register (IE).
--
-- Cross-validated against IRENA Renewable Capacity Statistics 2025
-- cumulative totals (within 10% per country, except where flagged in
-- the migration trailer notes).
--
-- China is intentionally excluded for offshore (and not in Tier 1 scope
-- for any class) per product decision: distortion + non-addressable
-- market for the asset-owner audience.

